    "department": "Silver.dev",
    "description": "ABOUT SILVER.DEV\n\nSilver.dev is a talent agency focused on connecting Startups with talent in Argentina and Uruguay.\n\nWe advocate for quality and craftsmanship, and we provide technical screening for companies in our portfolio. Our pass rate is low - we filter most candidates we interview and wish to keep the bar high to satisfy our promise to clients of providing low-volume high-quality candidates.\n\n\nWHAT WE ARE LOOKING FOR\n\nWe are looking for technical interviews that take up 45-minute coding sessions with candidates for our most demanding positions.\n\nWe want technical interviewers who pass the interview they give, as well as provide feedback to candidates.\n\nYou will be using Coderbyte and Ashby to assess candidates in our pool, and possibly more opportunities.\n\n\nREQUIREMENTS\n\n - 3 years of experience or more in a Product Startup or equivalent experience\n\n - Experience passing Live coding interviews at companies\n\n - Fluent in a popular language (javascript, python, ruby, etc) for Backend Challenges\n\n - Fluent in Frontend and React for Frontend Challenges\n\n\nINTERVIEW PROCESS\n\n - Silver.dev Technical Interview + Screening (1hr)",
